name: G4 spy ship
description:
The G4 is the ultra-fast command spacecraft in Area 51.
The G4 is a new generation of stealth spacecraft that is difficult to see and detect in the sky.
General Jia is in charge of it temporarily, the G4's task is to react quickly to the dangerous movements of the enemy near our borders, 3 G4 nuclear engines make it possible to get close to the borders in the shortest possible time.
